g (snooker player)|Warren King]]|4\n<!--Match8  -->\n|20 & 21 April|{{Flagicon|Canada}} '''[[Cliff Thorburn]] (4)'''|'''10'''|{{Flagicon|Canada}} [[Kirk Stevens]]|6\n<!--Match9  -->\n|20 & 21 April|{{Flagicon|England}} '''[[Neal Foulds]] (3)'''|'''10'''|{{Flagicon|Wales}} [[Wayne Jones (snooker player)|Wayne Jones]]|7\n<!--Match10  -->\n|20 April|{{Flagicon|Wales}} '''[[Doug Mountjoy]] (14)'''|'''10'''|{{Flagicon|England}} [[Barry West]]|6\n<!--Match11  -->\n|19 April|{{Flagicon|England}} '''[[Willie Thorne]] (11)'''|'''10'''|{{Flagicon|South Africa|1928}} [[Peter Francisco (snooker player)|Peter Francisco]]|6\n<!--Match12  -->\n|18 & 19 April|{{Flagicon|Wales}} '''[[Terry Griffiths]] (6)'''|'''10'''|{{Flagicon|England}} [[Steve Longworth]]|1\n<!--Match13  -->\n|17 & 18 April|{{Flagicon|England}} '''[[Tony Knowles (snooker player)|Tony Knowles]] (7)'''|'''10'''|{{Flagicon|England}} [[Danny Fowler]]|8\n<!--Match14  -->\n|17 & 18 April|{{Flagicon|South Africa|1928}} [[Silvino Francisco]] (10)|7|{{Flagicon|Australia}} '''[[Eddie Charlton]]'''|'''10'''\n<!--Match15  -->\n|16 & 17 April|{{Flagicon|England}} [[Dean Reynolds]] (15)|6|{{Flagicon|Scotland}} '''[[Stephen Hendry]]'''|'''10'''\n<!--Match16  -->\n|16 April|{{Flagicon|England}} '''[[Jimmy White]] (2)'''|'''10'''|{{Flagicon|Australia}} [[John Campbell (snooker player)|John Campbell]]|3\n<!-- LAST 16 -->\n<!--Match1  -->\n|21 & 22 April|{{Flagicon|England}} '''[[Steve Davis]] (1)'''|'''13'''|{{Flagicon|England}} [[Mike Hallett]] (16)|1\n<!--Match2  -->\n|22 & 23 April|{{Flagicon|Malta}} '''[[Tony Drago]]'''|'''13'''|{{Flagicon|Northern Ireland}} [[Dennis Taylor]] (8)|5\n<!--Match3  -->\n|23, 24 & 25 April|{{Flagicon|England}} [[Joe Johnson (snooker player)|Joe Johnson]] (5)|9|{{Flagicon|England}} '''[[Steve James (snooker player)|Steve James]]'''|'''13'''\n<!--Match4  -->\n|24 & 25 April|{{Flagicon|England}} [[John Parrott]] (13)|10|{{Flagicon|Canada}} '''[[Cliff Thorburn]] (4)'''|'''13'''\n<!--Match5  -->\n|24 & 2